# 404:DAILY FACTS Clothing Store

This is a modern, single-page e-commerce website for the 404:DAILY FACTS streetwear brand. The site is built using only HTML, CSS (Tailwind CSS), and JavaScript, and runs entirely in the browser with no backend required.

## Features

- Responsive, mobile-friendly design
- Product catalog with real clothing images and prices
- Add to cart, view cart, and checkout functionality
- User authentication (login/register) before purchase
- Multi-step checkout: delivery details and payment details
- All data stored in browser (localStorage)
- Brand identity and quotes featured throughout

## How to Run

1. Download or clone this repository.
2. Place all image files (product photos and logo) in the same folder as `index.html`.
3. Open `index.html` in your web browser (double-click or right-click > Open with... > your browser).

## Technologies Used

- **HTML**: Page structure
- **Tailwind CSS**: Styling and layout (via CDN)
- **JavaScript**: Product logic, cart, authentication, and checkout

## Folder Structure

```
/ (project root)
	|-- index.html
	|-- README
	|-- Daily Facts Logo.jpg
	|-- [other product images].jpg
```

## Usage

- Browse products and add items to your cart.
- Click the cart icon to view your cart and proceed to checkout.
- You must log in or register before purchasing.
- Enter delivery and payment details to complete your order.

## Customization

- To add or change products, edit the `products` array in `index.html`.
- To update branding or quotes, edit the hero and about sections in `index.html`.

## Disclaimer

This is a demo project for showcasing a clothing brand. No real payments are processed and all data is stored locally in your browser.